item.title: SoftLayer_Hardware_Chassis
item.description: SoftLayer_Hardware_Chassis Datatype Description Every piece of hardware in SoftLayer’s datacenters, including customer servers, are housed in one of many hardware chassis. The SoftLayer_Hardware_Chassis data type defines these chassis. Local formFactorId A hardware form factor internal identifier. Type: integer id A hardware chassis' internal identifier. Type: integer manufacturer A hardware chassis' manufacturer. Type: string name A hardware chassis' name.
